OL,3,CPrison officials face scrutiny as
OL,4,Cfamily alleges mistreatment
OL,6,FThe mother of a prisoner who died
OL,7,Fwhile on remand at HMP Swansea is
OL,8,Fdemanding answers regarding the
OL,9,Fcircumstances surrounding his death,
OL,10,Falleging her son was mistreated.
OL,12,FKian Parmee, 22, from Porth in Rhondda
OL,13,FCynon Taf, was discovered unresponsive
OL,14,Fin his cell at HMP Swansea on Sunday,
OL,15,F13 July.
OL,17,FHe was rushed to hospital that evening
OL,18,Fbut died due to his injuries five days
OL,19,Flater.
