OL,3,CPrison officials face scrutiny as
OL,4,Cfamily alleges mistreatment
OL,6,FPrison officials informed his mother,
OL,7,FNicola Parmee, that Kian had attempted
OL,8,Fto take his own life shortly after his
OL,9,Farrival at the Category B/C prison on
OL,10,FOystermouth Road. Ms. Parmee says her
OL,11,Fson never recovered from the injuries
OL,12,Fsustained that evening.
OL,14,FHowever, Ms. Parmee strongly disputes
OL,15,Fthe official account of her son's
OL,16,Fdeath, believing her son did not take
OL,17,Fhis own life and instead suspects
OL,18,Fmistreatment.
