OL,3,CPrison officials face scrutiny as
OL,4,Cfamily alleges mistreatment
OL,6,FKian Parmee's death is currently under
OL,7,Finvestigation by the Prison and
OL,8,FProbation Ombudsman. An inquest into
OL,9,Fhis death is due to open early next
OL,10,Fyear, with the circumstances
OL,11,Fsurrounding his death still unknown.
OL,13,F"He's a mammy's boy, he told me
OL,14,Feverything, he was my best friend as
OL,15,Fwell," Nicola told ITV News.
