OL,3,CPrison officials face scrutiny as
OL,4,Cfamily alleges mistreatment
OL,6,FKian Parmee appeared at Merthyr
OL,7,FMagistrates' Court on Wednesday, July
OL,8,F9, facing a charge of stalking without
OL,9,Fcausing fear, alarm, or distress. He
OL,10,Fhad been remanded to Swansea Prison,
OL,11,Fawaiting an appearance at Merthyr
OL,12,FCrown Court later this month.
OL,14,FMs. Parmee stated that despite mental
OL,15,Fhealth struggles in the days leading
OL,16,Fup to his initial court appearance,
OL,17,FKian appeared optimistic about his
OL,18,Ffuture while at HMP Swansea.
