OL,6,FKian Parmee's grandmother, Lyn Quick,
OL,7,Fhas raised serious concerns, alleging
OL,8,Fprison officials provided conflicting
OL,9,Finformation regarding the frequency of
OL,10,Fchecks on Kian during his time at the
OL,11,Ffacility.
OL,13,FShe also criticised staff for leaving
OL,14,FKian in a cell by himself,
OL,15,Fparticularly, she says, as it was his
OL,16,Ffirst time in prison.
