OL,6,F"As a family, we are determined, and
OL,7,FKian's name is never going to be
OL,8,Fforgotten; it's going to be out there,
OL,9,Fand everyone is going to know what has
OL,10,Fhappened to him. The truth will come
OL,11,Fout, I want the truth to come out, not
OL,12,Flies.
OL,14,F"I don't believe anybody, and I don't
OL,15,Ftrust anyone. My trust in the system
OL,16,Fis non-existent. We can't fetch Kian
OL,17,Fback, we want justice for Kian, but we
OL,18,Falso want to help and protect other
OL,19,Fpeople as well, and not for anyone
OL,20,Felse to go through what we are going
OL,21,Fthrough."
