OL,6,FIn response to the family's
OL,7,Fstatements, a Prison Service
OL,8,Fspokesperson offered their
OL,9,Fcondolences, saying: "Our thoughts
OL,10,Fremain with the friends and family of
OL,11,FKian Parmee."
OL,13,FThey added: "As with all deaths in
OL,14,Fcustody, the Prison and Probation
OL,15,FOmbudsman will investigate. It would
OL,16,Fbe inappropriate to comment further at
OL,17,Fthis stage."
